OL,3,CRestaurant fined for putting sheep
OL,4,Cmeat in ostrich curry
OL,6,FAn Indian takeaway has been fined
OL,7,Fafter selling an ostrich curry dish to
OL,8,Ftrading standards officers which was
OL,9,Flater found to contain sheep meat.
OL,11,FAbdul Malik Ali, of Amalik Cafe Ltd in
OL,12,FThirsk, pleaded guilty to offences
OL,13,Funder the Food Safety Act when he
OL,14,Fappeared at York Magistrates' Court on
OL,15,FFriday.
