OL,3,CRestaurant fined for putting sheep
OL,4,Cmeat in ostrich curry
OL,6,FAli ran the Jaipur Spice takeaway
OL,7,Frestaurant at the Busby Stoop Inn when
OL,8,FNorth Yorkshire Council's trading
OL,9,Fstandards officers visited in December
OL,10,F2023 and bought a meal described as an
OL,11,Fostrich curry.
OL,13,FBut when the dish was tested, it was
OL,14,Ffound to contain sheep meat instead of
OL,15,Fostrich.
OL,17,FAli told the court in his defence that
OL,18,Fa temporary chef had mistakenly
OL,19,Fselected the wrong meat during
OL,20,Fpreparation of the meal, North
OL,21,FYorkshire Council said.
