OL,6,FAli was handed a #237 fine and ordered
OL,7,Fto pay a further #400 in costs and a
OL,8,F#95 victim surcharge.
OL,10,FAmalik Cafe Ltd was fined #120 and was
OL,11,Fordered to pay #672 costs and a _48
OL,12,Fvictim surcharge.
OL,14,FNorth Yorkshire Council's executive
OL,15,Fmember for regulatory services,
OL,16,Fcouncillor Greg White, said:
OL,17,F"Consumers should not be subject to
OL,18,Fthis or any kind of food fraud.
